Description: Ravenpaw and Barley have lost their farm to a pack of vicious cats. They turn to the Thunderclan for help, but they have their own problems.
Title: WARRIORS: CLAN IN NEED
Author: Erin Hunter and James Barry
Contributor: by Erin Hunter and James Barry

Description: Kimihiro is having disturbing dream of the witch Yûko vanishing forever.
Title: XXXHOLIC, VOL. 15
Author: Clamp

Description: Naruto learns more secrets from his past and moves closer to discovering the identity of his nemesis, Pain.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 47
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 30
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 9
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: The Fairy Tail are a group of powerful wizards that includes the tough-fighter Erza Scarlet. This volume delves into her past and an impending doom.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 10
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 1
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Even a summer break will not stop the SOS brigade’s mission: to meet aliens, time travelers and psychics. It’s not your ordinary after-school club.
Title: THE MELANCHOLY OF HARUHI SUZUMIYA, VOL. 5
Author: Nagaru Tanigawa, Gaku Tsugano and Noizi Ito
Contributor: by Nagaru Tanigawa, Gaku Tsugano and Noizi Ito

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 2
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Alice’s exploration of this strange wonderland continues. In this world, everyone has clocks for hearts. Because they can be easily repaired, life is valued less.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS, VOL. 2
Author: Quinrose and Soumei Hoshino
